      <view class='index-docimg'>
        <image src='../../images/home-hd-docimg.png'></image>
      </view>
      <view class='index-docinfo'>
        <view class='index-docinfo-top'>
          <image class='index-docinfo-infobg' src='../../images/home-hd-infobox.png'></image>
          <view class='index-docinfo-toptext'>
            <view class='index-docinfo-text1'>
              <view class='index-docinfo-docname'>林朝胜</view>
              <view class='index-docinfo-zc'>主任医师</view>
              <view class='index-docinfo-line'>|</view>
              <view class='index-docinfo-keshi'>心血科</view>
            </view>
            <view class='index-docinfo-hosname'>重庆康华众联心血管病医院</view>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class='index-docinfo-bottom'>
          擅长:
          <view class='index-docinfo-bottomtext'>
            心血管疾病的诊治，尤其为高血压、 冠心病、心律失常、心功能不全患者提出 合理用药方案心血管疾病的诊治，尤其为高血压、 冠心病、心律失常、心功能不全患者提出 合理用药方案心血管疾病的诊治，尤其为高血压、 冠心病、心律失常、心功能不全患者提出 合理用药方案
